One person died and three were injured multi-vehicle crash involving two trucks and a car on the N3, between Tugela Plaza and Van Reenen’s Pass, in the northern KwaZulu-Natal on Sunday afternoon. Spokesperson for the KZN EMS, Robert McKenzie said three people were critically injured and treated at the scene before transported to the hospital. “The exact circumstances resulting in this crash are not know at this stage and are investigated by the police,” said McKenzie.